cleric.name: Cleric
cleric.description: The Cleric can heal a wounded character on an adjacent square for 1 action.

goblin.name: Goblin
goblin.description: The Goblin worth 2 VP for his owner when he escapes from the labyrinth.

mekanork.name: Mekanork
mekanork.description: A Mekanork standing on a Rotation Gear is able to rotate the rooms in any direction.

thief.name: Thief
thief.description: The Thief can open and close Portcullis. The Thief can move over and stop on Pit Traps. While the Thief stands on a Pit Trap, other characters of the same color can move over the Pit Trap without any difficulty.

warrior.name: Warrior
warrior.description: A Warrior standing in front of a closed Portcullis can break it for 1 AP.

troll.name: Troll
troll.description: When wounded, the Troll can regenerate for 1 AP.

wizard.name: Wizard
wizard.description: The Wizard has the permanent Special Ability of Levitation which allows him to move over Pit Traps and enemy characters

wall-walker.name: Wall-Walker
wall-walker.description: The Wall-Walker can walk through a wall for 1 AP.

armor.name: Armor
armor.description: The Combat value of a character wearing Armor is increased by 1 point (for defense only).

rope.name: Rope
rope.description: A character carrying a Rope can move over and stop on Pit Traps during his turn.

fireballwand.name: Fireball Wand
fireballwand.description: Only the Wizard can use the Fireball Wand. The Fireball immediately eliminates the first character (living or wounded) in the line of sight of the Wizard using the wand.

speedpotion.name: Speed potion
speedpotion.description: A character carrying a Speed Potion can drink it for 1 AP. This character immediately receives 4 AP that he must use during the current turn.

sword.name: Sword
sword.description: The Combat value of a character carrying a Sword is increased by 1 point (for attack only).

treasure.name: Treasure
treasure.description: A Treasure earns a player 1 VP if one of his characters is carrying it when he leaves the labyrinth.
